@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gybyko(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.89
    v2 = (wp.abs(v1) * wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.47)))
    v1 = (0.04 - wp.abs((v2 + 0.49 + tmp + 0.24)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp))
    tmp = (v0 / (wp.exp(v1 + 0.41) / wp.sin(v0 + 0.44)))
    data[tid] = v0
